sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Doctor
    participant UI as React Client
    participant API as ASP.NET API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Blob as S3/Blob Storage
    participant AI as FastAPI (AI Engine)
    participant LLM as OpenAI (LLM Engine)

    Doctor->>UI: Upload X-Ray Image
    activate UI
    UI->>API: POST /api/studies/{id}/images (Multipart)
    activate API
    API->>Blob: Upload X-ray file
    activate Blob
    Blob-->>API: secure_URL
    deactivate Blob
    API->>DB: Insert XRayImage record
    API-->>UI: 201 Created (imageId)
    deactivate API
    
    Doctor->>UI: Click "Run AI Analysis"
    UI->>API: POST /api/images/{id}/analyze
    activate API
    API->>DB: Create AnalysisSession (Status=Processing)
    API-->>UI: 202 Accepted (sessionId)
    deactivate API
    UI-->>Doctor: Progress Indicator (Polling)
    deactivate UI

    Note over API,LLM: Background AI Pipeline Execution

    API->>AI: POST /ai/detect-landmarks {imageUrl}
    activate AI
    AI->>Blob: Fetch image file
    AI->>AI: Inference HRNet Model
    AI-->>API: List[Landmarks, Confidences]
    deactivate AI
    API->>DB: Bulk Insert Landmarks

    API->>AI: POST /ai/calculate-measurements {landmarks}
    activate AI
    AI->>AI: Compute Geometry (SNA, ANB, IMPA...)
    AI-->>API: List[Measurements]
    deactivate AI
    API->>DB: Bulk Insert Measurements

    API->>AI: POST /ai/classify-diagnosis {measurements}
    activate AI
    AI->>AI: Rule-based Classification Mapping
    AI-->>API: Diagnosis Classification Output
    deactivate AI
    API->>DB: Insert Diagnosis Record

    API->>AI: POST /ai/suggest-treatment {diagnosis}
    activate AI
    AI->>LLM: Request clinical justification via prompt
    activate LLM
    LLM-->>AI: Clinical Rationale Generation (Text Stream)
    deactivate LLM
    AI-->>API: TreatmentPlans Array (Primary & Alternatives)
    deactivate AI
    API->>DB: Insert TreatmentPlans

    API->>DB: Update Session (Status=Completed)

    Note over Doctor,UI: Client receives completion status
    Doctor->>UI: View Results
    activate UI
    UI->>API: GET /sessions/{id}/results
    activate API
    API-->>UI: 200 OK (Full Analysis payload)
    deactivate API
    UI-->>Doctor: Render Landmarks Canvas & Measurements Table
    deactivate UI